<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Order Status Update - QuickBite</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f7f7f7;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        color: #333;
      }

      .email-container {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 40px;
        margin: 30px auto;
        border-radius: 10px;
        max-width: 700px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 24px;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .status {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #4CAF50;
        font-size: 18px;
      }

      .order-details {
        margin-top: 25px;
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      .order-details h3 {
        font-size: 20px;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      .order-details ul {
        list-style-type: none;
        padding-left: 0;
      }

      .order-details li {
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: #555;
      }

      .order-summary {
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 15px;
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      .order-summary p {
        margin: 0;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #333;
      }

      .footer1 {
        margin-top: 30px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #aaa;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .footer1 a {
        color: #4CAF50;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .btn {
        background-color: #4CAF50;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        font-size: 16px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }

      .btn:hover {
        background-color: #45a049;
      }

      .highlight {
        color: #4CAF50;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <h2>Hello {{firstName}},</h2>
      <p>
        We’re excited to inform you that your order <strong>#{{orderId}}</strong>
        has been updated! Below are the latest details:
      </p>
      <p>
        Current Status: <span class="status">{{orderStatus}}</span>
      </p>

      <div class="order-details">
        <h3>Order Details</h3>
        <ul>
          {{#each items}}
          <li>
            <strong>{{this.name}}</strong> — Quantity: {{this.quantity}}
          </li>
          {{/each}}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="order-summary">
        <p>Total Amount: <span class="highlight">${{amount}}</span></p>
        <p>Estimated Delivery: <span class="highlight">{{estimatedDelivery}}</span></p>
      </div>

      <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance, feel free to reach out to our dedicated support team. We're here to help!</p>

      <p>
        Thank you for choosing QuickBite! We look forward to serving you again soon.
      </p>

      <a href="https://quickbite-eta.vercel.app/" class="btn">Contact Support</a>

      <div class="footer1">
        <p>&copy; {{year}} QuickBite. All rights reserved.</p>


      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
